 be repaired within 24-48 hours of being received at our facility if there is an issue with the repair that will take longer than this time NJPhonefix.com will contact the customer and inform them. At this point customer has the right to refuse repair, if customer refuses repair the device will be shipped back and a full refund will be issued.</li>\r\n	<li>Our experienced technicians perform a full inspection of the devices before being repaired and after a repair has been performed. All repairs take place in our facility by NJPhonefix.com employees only.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong><strong>Warranty</strong></strong>\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n	<li>All devices are covered by a 60 day warranty for the repair that we have performed. This is only valid if the parts that we replaced stop working not if it was physically damaged by the user.</li>\r\n	<li>We are not responsible for data being lost including photos, contacts, messages or any other personal data. It is very rare that we have to reset a device but there are situations where that may be the only solution, customers will be informed of that prior to performing that kind of repair.</li>\r\n	<li>If damage is detected on a device that was not paid for by the customer we will contact the customer and check if they wish to continue with the repair. If customer chooses not to continue with the repair that device will not be covered by our warranty. The customer has the right to refuse to repair the original problem, if this happens the device will be returned and a refund will be issued except for shipping cost.</li>\r\n	<li>If our technicians accidently break something we will be fully responsible for replacing the damaged part without any cost to the customer. If the damage is unfixable we will provide a refurbished device as a replacement.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong><strong>Shipping</strong></strong>\r\n<ol start=\"11\">\r\n	<li>NJPhonefix.com is not responsible for devices that are damaged during mail or that are not sent without any tracking information. NJPhonefix.com will not be responsible for devices that are lost or stolen in the mail.</li>\r\n	<li>Return shipping on all cell phone is free. We use USPS first class mail with tracking information. Additional shipping options are available for purchase.</li>\r\n	<li>When shipping devices to NJPhonefix.com please do not include any accessories unless it is a laptop in which case the only thing that should be attached to it is the charger. If accessories are shipped with cell phones and tablets they will not be returned unless customer pays for return shipping.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong><strong>Returns and Exchanges</strong></strong>\r\n<ol start=\"14\">\r\n	<li>All repair parts or kits from NJPhonefix.com are sold “AS IS” due to the complexity of the repairs. All parts and kits are tested before being shipped and are in working order.  Replacement parts are intended for experienced technicians and a return or exchange will be issued in a case by case basis. NJPhonefix.com has the right to refuse returns or exchanges to anyone.</li>\r\n</ol>','Terms and Conditions','','publish','open','open','','terms-and-conditions','','','2012-05-24 15:33:24','2012-05-24 19:33:24','',0,'http://njphonefix.com/?page_id=584',0,'page','',0),(765,1,'2012-05-24 15:27:28','2012-05-24 19:27:28','<a href=\"http://njphonefix.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Smart-Phones.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-606\" title=\"Smart Phones\" src=\"http://njphonefix.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Smart-Phones.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"184\" height=\"140\" /></a>\r\nNJ Phone Fix is the leading cell phone repair company in New Jersey. Enjoy our fast turnaround time (24-48 hours) for mail in repairs or bring your cell phone, tablet or laptop to our walk in locations in North Jersey. We Repair cell Phones from all manufacturers “Apple” “HTC” “Blackberry” “Samsung” “LG” “Motorola” “Nokia”. If the repair you need is not listed on this website, simply call or email