ing options are available for purchase.</li>\n	<li>When shipping devices to NJPhonefix.com please do not include any accessories unless it is a laptop in which case the only thing that should be attached to it is the charger. If accessories are shipped with cell phones and tablets they will not be returned unless customer pays for return shipping.</li>\n</ol>\n<strong><strong>Returns and Exchanges</strong></strong>\n<ol start=\"14\">\n	<li>All repair parts or kits from NJPhonefix.com are sold “AS IS” due to the complexity of the repairs. All parts and kits are tested before being shipped and are in working order.  Replacement parts are intended for experienced technicians and a return or exchange will be issued in a case by case basis. NJPhonefix.com has the right to refuse returns or exchanges to anyone.</li>\n</ol>','Terms and Conditions','','inherit','open','open','','584-revision','','','2012-04-24 11:18:27','2012-04-24 15:18:27','',584,'http://njphonefix.com/2012/04/24/584-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(586,1,'2012-04-24 11:27:38','2012-04-24 15:27:38','This service is for an iPhone 3g/3gs glass digitizer repair. Purchase this service if your glass screen is cracked or it is no longer responding to touch.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"internal-source-marker_0.24385536462068558\">If you have any question about any repair please call us or bring the phone to our local location. All of our repairs are backed by a 60 day warranty policy. We strive to perform the best quality repair to satisfy our customers as well as a fast turnaround, because we know how important your phone is.</strong>','iPhone 3g/3gs Glass Digitizer Repair','','publish','closed','closed','','iphone-3g3gs-glass-digitizer-repair','','','2012-06-02 11:40:01','2012-06-02 15:40:01','',0,'http://njphonefix.com/products/uncategorized/',0,'wpsc-product','',0),(587,1,'2012-04-24 11:27:31','2012-04-24 15:27:31','','iPhone 3g 3gs glass digitizer repair','','inherit','open','open','','iphone-3g-3gs-glass-digitizer-r